  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_e9533adb563336ae4c48055d023dea66">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>Collection contains documents relating to the founding of Delta Sigma Theta and the Cornell University formerly Theta Chapter now Mu Gamma chapter, publications, clippings, ephemera, and other material relating to Delta Sigma Theta Sorority Incorporated.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite audience="internal" id="aspace_1b2a430c8886287335b5b40e36f37dac">
